general.desc: Jikai Equipment Manufacturing Co Ltd Is engaged in the development, manufacture, distribution and service of underground mining machinery. It provides specialized solutions in underground mining industry for tunneling, tunnel supporting and transportation and others. The main products consist of Tunnel Supporting Equipment's and tools, Tunnel Safety Equipment's and accessories, Road Header and Heavy-Duty Scraper Conveyor and others. Geographically, the business activities are carried out through the region of China.
general.short_desc: Jikai Equipment Manufacturing Co Ltd, formerly Shijiazhuang Zhongmei Coal Mine Equipment Manufacture Co Ltd develops, manufactures and sells supporting equipment, safety drillers, tunneling equipment and transportation machinery.
